    [::Queue::__finally__] method, it can be used in a
    `using` block:

        using (var q = emitter.queue()) {
          while (true) {
            var data = q.get();
            ...
          }
        }

    Here the `using` construct will automatically call
    [::Queue::stop] when the `using` code
    block is exited.

